OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FBlustery with patchy light rain
OL,6,Fgiving way to heavy and persistent
OL,7,Frain for the afternoon. Windy in many
OL,8,Fcoastal regions and over the hills
OL,9,Fwith a chance of gales in exposed
OL,10,Fspots. Not as mild, but temperatures
OL,11,Fstill above average.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FRain should become confined
OL,14,Fto southernmost areas during the
OL,15,Fevening and overnight, with drier,
OL,16,Fthough still rather cloudy weather
OL,17,Felsewhere. Winds becoming light.
OL,18,FCooler than last night, but frost free.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
