OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CFriday:FSouthern areas could see
OL,6,Foccasional outbreaks of rain on
OL,7,FFriday. Further north it looks mostly
OL,8,Fdry, with brighter breaks. Very mild
OL,9,Fwith light winds, though feeling
OL,10,Fcooler in any rain.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:
OL,13,FOvernight rain, perhaps with some hill
OL,14,Fsnow, giving way to brighter skies on
OL,15,FSaturday. Turning damp and windy on
OL,16,FSunday. Brighter, but still showery
OL,17,Fand breezy on Monday. Briefly cooler.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
